text: The Psycho-Social, Chemical, Biological & Electro-Magnetic Manipulation of Human Consciousness is the first studio album by American underground hip hop group, Jedi Mind Tricks. It was released on November 4, 1997 through Superegular Records. It was re-released in 2003 through Babygrande Records. The producer of the album was Stoupe the Enemy of Mankind. The album is sometimes called The Psycho-Social CD for short. ==Songs== ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1997 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Jedi Mind Tricks albums Category:Hip hop albums
